d space-y-1\"><a href=\"tel:+998770802288\" class=\"text-white font-semibold hover:text-teal-500 transition text-sm\">+998 77 080 22 88</a><a href=\"tel:+998974802288\" class=\"text-gray-300 text-xs hover:text-teal-500 transition\">+998 97 480 22 88</a></div><button class=\"lg:hidden text-white p-2\" aria-label=\"Открыть меню\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-navigation\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><main id=\"main-content\" class=\"pt-20\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"Korporativ sovg'alar 2025: O'zbekistonda to'liq gid\",\"description\":\"Xodimlar, hamkorlar va mijozlar uchun sovg'ani to'g'ri tanlang. Byudjet, g'oya, gravirovka. Hisob-kitob so'rang!\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/korporativ-sovgalar-toliq-gid-2025-uzbekistan\",\"image\":\"/images/blog/korporativ-sovgalar-toliq-gid-2025-uzbekistan.jpg\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-03-03\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-03-03\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/logo192.png\"}},\"mainEntityOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/korporativ-sovgalar-toliq-gid-2025-uzbekistan\"}}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Blog\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Korporativ sovg'alar 2025: O'zbekistonda to'liq gid\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/korporativ-sovgalar-toliq-gid-2025-uzbekistan\"}]}</script><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><nav aria-label=\"breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-8\"><ol class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-400 flex-wrap gap-y-1\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz\">Graver.uz</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 truncate max-w-xs\">Korporativ sovg&#x27;alar 2025: O&#x27;zbekistonda to&#x27;liq gid</li></ol></nav><header class=\"mb-10\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight\">Korporativ sovg&#x27;alar 2025: O&#x27;zbekistonda to&#x27;liq gid</h1><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4 text-sm text-gray-500\"><time dateTime=\"2026-03-03\">2-mart, 2026</time><span>2<!-- --> <!-- -->daqiqa o&#x27;qish</span><span>Graver.uz</span></div></header><div class=\"mb-10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/images/blog/korporativ-sovgalar-toliq-gid-2025-uzbekistan.jpg\" alt=\"Korporativ sovg&#x27;alar 2025: O&#x27;zbekistonda to&#x27;liq gid\" class=\"w-full aspect-video object-cover\" loading=\"eager\"/></div><article class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p>Korporativ sovg&#x27;a - bu xarajat emas, signal. U ichki motivatsiyani ham, tashqi sheriklikni ham mustahkamlaydi. Ushbu 2025 gid: kimga nima berish, byudjet, etiket va lazer gravirovka orqali qanday premium effekt qilish.</p>\n<h2>1) Sovg&#x27;a strategiyasi: avval maqsadni aniqlang</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Ichki maqsadlar: loyallik, eNPS, onboarding, yubiley/KPI</li>\n<li>Tashqi maqsadlar: hamkorlikni mustahkamlash, &quot;top-of-mind&quot;, PR/ko&#x27;rgazma</li>\n<li>Qoidasi: bir xil buyum turli auditoriyada turlicha ishlaydi</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>2) Kimga sovg&#x27;a: 3 asosiy segment</h2>\n<h3>Xodimlar (HR yo&#x27;nalishi)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tug&#x27;ilgan kun, yubiley, KPI, yangi loyiha yakuni</li>\n<li>Welcome pack va jamoa merch</li>\n<li>Shaxsiylashtirish: ism bilan gravirovka</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Hamkorlar va mijozlar (B2B)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Status darajasi bo&#x27;yicha: top/middle/operatsion</li>\n<li>Etiket: haddan tashqari shaxsiy yoki juda arzon sovg&#x27;adan qochish</li>\n<li>&quot;Uzoq yashaydigan&quot; buyumlar: soat, ruchka, setlar</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Tadbirlar (event)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Ko&#x27;rgazma/summit uchun bir xil tiraj</li>\n<li>Yengil, tashishga qulay, brend ko&#x27;rinishi aniq</li>\n<li>QR-kodli kartalar/aksessuarlar (lead tracking)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>3) Byudjet: diapazonlar va &quot;value&quot; qoidasi</h2>\n<p>Byudjetni &quot;so&#x27;m&quot; bilan emas, &quot;qabul qiluvchi uchun qiymat&quot; bilan o&#x27;lchang. Katta logo qo&#x27;yib arzon buyumni qimmatga aylantirib bo&#x27;lmaydi. Aksincha, o&#x27;rtacha buyum to&#x27;g&#x27;ri qadoq + gravirovka bilan premium ko&#x27;rinadi.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Byudjet: bazaviy (tiraj katta) / standart (ko&#x27;p holat) / premium (VIP)</li>\n<li>Qadoqlash har doim ta&#x27;sir qiladi: unboxing - marketing</li>\n<li>Shaxsiylashtirish - eng kuchli multiplikator</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>4) Texnologiyalar: brending va lazer gravirovka</h2>\n<h3>Lazer gravirovka qachon ideal</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Metall: ruchka, termos, brelok, soat</li>\n<li>Yog&#x27;och: desk set, quti qopqog&#x27;i, stend</li>\n<li>Chidamlilik kerak bo&#x27;lsa: &quot;yuvilmaydi, o&#x27;chmaydi&quot;</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Print/UV/kashta qachon yaxshi</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tekstil merch (t-shirt, hoodie)</li>\n<li>Rangli grafikalar kerak bo&#x27;lsa</li>\n<li>Tez tiraj (ba&#x27;zan)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>5) Buyurtma jarayoni: Toshkentda 7 bosqich</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Brif: auditoriya, tiraj, byudjet, deadline</li>\n<li>Tanlov: 3-5 variant (narx/ta&#x27;sir)</li>\n<li>Maket: logo + gravirovka joylashuvi</li>\n<li>Namuna: 1-2 dona</li>\n<li>Ishlab chiqarish: gravirovka + komplektatsiya</li>\n<li>QC: sifat nazorati</li>\n<li>Yetkazish: ofis/tadbir joyi</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>6) Eng ko&#x27;p uchraydigan xatolar</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Noto&#x27;g&#x27;ri segment: xodimga &quot;hamkor sovg&#x27;asi&quot; berish</li>\n<li>Muddatsiz start: bayram oldidan oxirgi hafta</li>\n<li>Ro&#x27;yxat tartibsiz: ismlar xato gravirovka bo&#x27;ladi</li>\n<li>Yomon qadoqlash: premium buyum ham arzon ko&#x27;rinadi</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Buyurtma bermoqchimisiz?</strong> Telegram <a href=\"https://t.me/graveruz\">@graveruz</a> ga yozing yoki saytdagi shaklni to&#x27;ldiring.</p></article><section class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6\">O&#x27;xshash maqolalar</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/xodimlar-uchun-sovga-tanlash-chek-list\">Xodimlar uchun sovg&#x27;a tanlash: HR uchun chek-list | Graver Studio</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Xodimlar uchun korporativ sovg&#x27;a tanlash bo&#x27;yicha HR chek-listi: byudjet, shaxsiylashtirish, muddatlar va brendlash maslahatlar.</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/b2b-korporativ-sovga-tanlash\">B2B korporativ sovg&#x27;a tanlash: HR uchun qo&#x27;llanma</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">B2B segmentda korporativ sovg&#x27;a tanlash bo&#x27;yicha to&#x27;liq qo&#x27;llanma: mezonlar, byudjet va brendlash strategiyasi.</p></article></div></section><div class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-8\"><a class=\"text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-400 transition flex items-center\" href=\"/uz/blog\">← <!-- -->Blogga qaytish</a></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-black border-t border-gray-800 mt-20\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div><a class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4\" href=\"/uz\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-bold\">G</span></div><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Graver<span class=\"text-teal-500\">.uz</span></span></a><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm\">Toshkentda biznes uchun premium lazer o&#x27;ymakorlik va brendlash</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">Navigatsiya</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz#services\">Xizmatlar</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz/catalog-products\">Mahsulotlar</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz/contacts\">Aloqa</a></li></ul></div><div><h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">Aloqa</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a href=\"tel:+998770802288\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\">+998 77 080 22 88</a></li><li><a href=\"tel:+998974802288\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\">+998 97 480 22 88</a></li><li><a href=\"https://t.me/GraverAdm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\">Telegram</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm\">Toshkent, Mukimiy ko&#x27;chasi</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-gray-800 mt-8 pt-8 text-center\"><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Graver.uz. <!-- -->Barcha huquqlar himoyalangan<!-- -->.</p></div></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-68f22649503f8e75.js\" async=\"\"></