children\":\"Tashqi maqsadlar: hamkorlikni mustahkamlash, \\\"top-of-mind\\\", PR/ko'rgazma\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Qoidasi: bir xil buyum turli auditoriyada turlicha ishlaydi\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"2) Kimga sovg'a: 3 asosiy segment\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Xodimlar (HR yo'nalishi)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Tug'ilgan kun, yubiley, KPI, yangi loyiha yakuni\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Welcome pack va jamoa merch\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Shaxsiylashtirish: ism bilan gravirovka\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Hamkorlar va mijozlar (B2B)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Status darajasi bo'yicha: top/middle/operatsion\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Etiket: haddan tashqari shaxsiy yoki juda arzon sovg'adan qochish\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"\\\"Uzoq yashaydigan\\\" buyumlar: soat, ruchka, setlar\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Tadbirlar (event)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Ko'rgazma/summit uchun bir xil tiraj\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Yengil, tashishga qulay, brend ko'rinishi aniq\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"QR-kodli kartalar/aksessuarlar (lead tracking)\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"3) Byudjet: diapazonlar va \\\"value\\\" qoidasi\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Byudjetni \\\"so'm\\\" bilan emas, \\\"qabul qiluvchi uchun qiymat\\\" bilan o'lchang. Katta logo qo'yib arzon buyumni qimmatga aylantirib bo'lmaydi. Aksincha, o'rtacha buyum to'g'ri qadoq + gravirovka bilan premium ko'rinadi.\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Byudjet: bazaviy (tiraj katta) / standart (ko'p holat) / premium (VIP)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Qadoqlash har doim ta'sir qiladi: unboxing - marketing\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Shaxsiylashtirish - eng kuchli multiplikator\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"4) Texnologiyalar: brending va lazer gravirovka\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Lazer gravirovka qachon ideal\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Metall: ruchka, termos, brelok, soat\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Yog'och: desk set, quti qopqog'i, stend\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Chidamlilik kerak bo'lsa: \\\"yuvilmaydi, o'chmaydi\\\"\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Print/UV/kashta qachon yaxshi\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Tekstil merch (t-shirt, hoodie)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Rangli grafikalar kerak bo'lsa\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Tez tiraj (ba'zan)\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"5) Buyurtma jarayoni: Toshkentda 7 bosqich\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Brif: auditoriya, tiraj, byudjet, deadline\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Tanlov: 3-5 variant (narx/ta'sir)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Maket: logo + gravirovka joylashuvi\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Namuna: 1-2 dona\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Ishlab chiqarish: gravirovka + komplektatsiya\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"QC: sifat nazorati\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Yetkazish: ofis/tadbir joyi\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"6) Eng ko'p uchraydigan xatolar\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Noto'g'ri segment: xodimga \\\"hamkor sovg'asi\\